About.title: ABOUT
About.p1: Software engineer in progress, with experience in Front-End and growing proficiency in Back-End development. Specialized in technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, TypeScript, and Python, with a focus on frameworks like Django, Next.JS, Flask, and React.JS. I demonstrate my ability in diverse projects, ranging from institutional websites to complex web applications.

I am highly committed to continuous learning and making significant contributions to teams, offering creativity, problem-solving skills, and code quality.
